options.text: Are you going to sit there all day?

327491a4-9bde-4e17-8308-ea25583fe1ce.title: <player>
327491a4-9bde-4e17-8308-ea25583fe1ce.text: Are you going to sit there all day?

3f85075e-6846-4a8c-a90a-674b3e1978eb.title: Ahab
3f85075e-6846-4a8c-a90a-674b3e1978eb.text: Aye, I am. I canna walk, ye see.

bad58e26-7e9b-4c88-832d-b5df07857dc3.title: Ahab
bad58e26-7e9b-4c88-832d-b5df07857dc3.text:
Arrr, I 'ave only the one leg! I lost its twin when my
last ship went down.

022152d9-d4b7-4a66-ae38-349c92c4cf2c.title: <player>
022152d9-d4b7-4a66-ae38-349c92c4cf2c.text: But I can see both your legs!

6c03a011-bdaf-4948-9a04-158232b197c2.title: Ahab
6c03a011-bdaf-4948-9a04-158232b197c2.text:
Nay, young laddie, this be a false leg. For years I had
me a sturdy wooden peg-leg, but now I wear this
dainty little feller.

5d499286-1a28-4348-a9cf-897a707f23a2.title: Ahab
5d499286-1a28-4348-a9cf-897a707f23a2.text: Yon peg-leg kept getting stuck in the floorboards.

66ecefb4-ea1c-438e-9ef7-ce9e24fc4742.title: Ahab
66ecefb4-ea1c-438e-9ef7-ce9e24fc4742.text:
Perhaps a bright young laddie like yerself would like to
help me? I be needing another ship to go a-hunting my
enemy.

a31ae084-110d-495a-b421-2fe5f796d244.title: <player>
a31ae084-110d-495a-b421-2fe5f796d244.text: Hmmm. And can you afford another ship?

288cfcfb-af7d-4bdd-8c3d-93589c717d76.title: Ahab
288cfcfb-af7d-4bdd-8c3d-93589c717d76.text:
Nay, I have nary a penny to my name. All my worldly
goods went down with me old ship.

54f1e808-b527-4ea2-aae0-e5ce51fd70ab.title: <player>
54f1e808-b527-4ea2-aae0-e5ce51fd70ab.text: So you're actually asking me to give you a free ship.

030fcb8e-dc6c-4912-9079-6d530d31acc8.title: Ahab
030fcb8e-dc6c-4912-9079-6d530d31acc8.text: Arrr! Would ye be so kind?

ab0bf407-32ca-46aa-9306-924969a64823.title: <player>
ab0bf407-32ca-46aa-9306-924969a64823.text: Do you have anything for trade?

3517f65c-d1b3-4164-9da6-3aa686fcf76f.title: Ahab
3517f65c-d1b3-4164-9da6-3aa686fcf76f.text:
Nothin' at the moment, but then again the Customs
Agents are on the warpath right now.
